articles.title: UK, EU have an understanding on how to resolve Northern Ireland protocol, PM Sunak says - Reuters
articles.description: Britain's Rishi Sunak said "intensive work" was needed in coming days to reach a resolution to the Northern Ireland protocol issue after what he described as a positive discussion with European Commission President Ursula von der Leyen.
